<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="240" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[153,1038,1070,1226]" pageId="3" pageNumber="240">
There are three species of 
<taxonomicName box="[430,546,1114,1138]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Nemopoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[430,546,1114,1138]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="240">Nemopoda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
recorded for Switzerland but most records are from 
<taxonomicName box="[210,324,1143,1167]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Nemopoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nitidula">
<emphasis box="[210,324,1143,1167]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="240">N. nitidula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
,while 
<taxonomicName box="[401,551,1143,1167]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Nemopoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pectinulata">
<emphasis box="[401,551,1143,1167]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="240">N. pectinulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[602,715,1144,1167]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Nemopoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="speiseri">
<emphasis box="[602,715,1144,1167]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="240">N. speiseri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(not present in this collection) are less common. 
<taxonomicName box="[351,467,1173,1197]" class="Insecta" family="Platystomatidae" genus="Nemopoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="240" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[351,467,1173,1197]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="240">Nemopoda</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
spp. can occasionally be found on cow pastures but are particularly common on wet decaying animal tissue.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
